---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy">
  <div class="pt-32 pb-24 px-6 md:px-12 lg:px-24 max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <!-- Editorial Header Section -->
    <header class="mb-20">
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-4">
        <span class="font-label text-label-md uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-on-surface-variant font-semibold">Legal Documentation</span>
        <h1 class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-7xl font-extrabold tracking-tighter text-primary max-w-4xl">
          Privacy Policy / <br/>
          <span class="text-on-primary-container">Datenschutzerklärung</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="mt-6 font-body text-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl leading-relaxed">
          At Joodi Logistics, we are committed to global transparency. This document outlines how we orchestrate and protect your data across our logistics network.
        </p>
      </div>
    </header>
    <!-- Bento-style Content Grid -->
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-12">
      <!-- Sticky Sidebar for Quick Navigation -->
      <aside class="md:col-span-3 hidden md:block">
        <div class="sticky top-32 flex flex-col gap-6">
          <nav class="flex flex-col gap-4">
            <a class="text-primary font-semibold text-sm border-l-2 border-primary pl-4" href="#controller">Data Controller</a>
            <a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm border-l-2 border-transparent pl-4" href="#collection">Data Collection</a>
            <a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm border-l-2 border-transparent pl-4" href="#rights">Your Rights</a>
            <a class="text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors text-sm border-l-2 border-transparent pl-4" href="#security">Security</a>
          </nav>
          <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low rounded-xl">
            <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-sm text-primary mb-2">Need Help?</h4>
            <p class="text-xs text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">For specific inquiries regarding your data, please contact our privacy officer.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </aside>
      <!-- Main Policy Text -->
      <div class="md:col-span-9 flex flex-col gap-16">
        <!-- Section: Data Controller -->
        <section class="bg-surface-container-lowest p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl shadow-[0_20px_40px_rgba(25,28,30,0.04)]" id="controller">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-8">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-3xl" data-icon="account_balance">account_balance</span>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-2xl font-bold text-primary">1. Data Controller</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">Entity</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-lg font-semibold text-primary">Joodi Logistics</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant">123 Logistics Plaza<br/>Global Trade Zone<br/>Germany</p>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4">
              <h3 class="font-headline font-bold text-sm uppercase tracking-wider text-on-surface-variant">Legal Representative</h3>
              <p class="font-body text-lg font-semibold text-primary">John-Paul Odidika</p>
              <p class="font-body text-sm text-on-surface-variant">Chief Executive Officer</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Section: General GDPR Compliance -->
        <section class="space-y-8" id="collection">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-tertiary-container text-3xl" data-icon="security">security</span>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary">2. Information Collection and Use</h2>
          </div>
          <div class="prose prose-slate max-w-none space-y-6 text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            <p>While using our Service, we may ask you to provide us with certain personally identifiable information that can be used to contact or identify you ("Personal Data"). Personally identifiable information may include, but is not limited to:</p>
            <ul class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 list-none p-0">
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container p-4 rounded-lg">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl" data-icon="mail">mail</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Email address</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container p-4 rounded-lg">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl" data-icon="person">person</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">First name and last name</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container p-4 rounded-lg">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl" data-icon="call">call</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Phone number</span>
              </li>
              <li class="flex items-center gap-3 bg-surface-container p-4 rounded-lg">
                <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-primary text-xl" data-icon="location_on">location_on</span>
                <span class="text-sm font-medium">Address, State, ZIP/Postal code</span>
              </li>
            </ul>
            <p class="pt-4">We use this data to facilitate cross-border logistics operations, maintain customs compliance, and provide real-time tracking updates to our clients. The legal basis for processing is Art. 6 Para. 1 lit. b GDPR (Contract Fulfillment) and Art. 6 Para. 1 lit. f GDPR (Legitimate Interest).</p>
          </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Section: Log Data -->
        <section class="bg-primary text-on-primary p-12 rounded-2xl relative overflow-hidden" id="security">
          <div class="relative z-10">
            <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold mb-6">3. Technical Log Data</h2>
            <p class="text-on-primary-container leading-relaxed mb-8">
              We collect information that your browser sends whenever you visit our Service ("Log Data"). This Log Data may include information such as your computer's Internet Protocol ("IP") address, browser type, browser version, the pages of our Service that you visit, the time and date of your visit, the time spent on those pages and other statistics.
            </p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
              <span class="bg-primary-container text-white px-4 py-2 rounded font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">IP Anonymization Active</span>
              <span class="bg-primary-container text-white px-4 py-2 rounded font-label text-[10px] tracking-widest uppercase">SSL/TLS Encrypted</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <!-- Decorative Background Element -->
          <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 -mr-20 -mt-20 w-80 h-80 bg-on-primary-container/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
        </section>
        <!-- Section: Your Rights -->
        <section class="space-y-8" id="rights">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4 mb-4">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-on-tertiary-container text-3xl" data-icon="gavel">gavel</span>
            <h2 class="font-headline text-3xl font-extrabold tracking-tight text-primary">4. Your Rights under GDPR</h2>
          </div>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant">Under the General Data Protection Regulation, you have the following fundamental rights:</p>
          <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-b-2 border-primary-container">
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">Right to Rectification</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">You have the right to have your information rectified if that information is inaccurate or incomplete.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-b-2 border-tertiary-fixed-dim">
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">Right to Object</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">You have the right to object to our processing of your Personal Data.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-b-2 border-secondary">
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">Right of Restriction</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">You have the right to request that we restrict the processing of your personal information.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6 bg-surface-container-low border-b-2 border-on-secondary-container">
              <h4 class="font-headline font-bold text-primary mb-2">Data Portability</h4>
              <p class="text-sm text-on-surface-variant">You have the right to be provided with a copy of the information we have on you in a structured format.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </section>
        <!-- Section: Final Provisions -->
        <section class="border-t border-outline-variant pt-12">
          <h2 class="font-headline text-xl font-bold text-primary mb-4">Changes To This Privacy Policy</h2>
          <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed">
            We may update our Privacy Policy from time to time. We will notify you of any changes by posting the new Privacy Policy on this page. You are advised to review this Privacy Policy periodically for any changes.
          </p>
          <div class="mt-8 flex items-center gap-2 text-on-surface-variant">
            <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm" data-icon="update">update</span>
            <span class="font-label text-xs uppercase tracking-wider">Last Updated: October 24, 2024</span>
          </div>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
